---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="px-6 md:px-12 py-10 bg-ink">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">

    <p class="font-display font-bold text-[20px] tracking-tight text-white">
      Orchard
    </p>

    <p class="font-body text-[13px] text-white/35 text-center order-last md:order-none">
      Del huerto a tu mesa en horas, no días.
    </p>

    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-white/25 tracking-[0.06em]">
      © {year}
    </p>

  </div>
</footer>
